gov.va.med.srcalc.web.view.admin

Class EditBaseVar

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.med.srcalc.web.view.admin.EditBaseVar
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EditVar
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EditAbstractNumericalVar, EditBooleanVar, EditMultiSelectVar

    public abstract class EditBaseVar
extends java.lang.Object
implements EditVar

    Stores basic AbstractVariable properties for creating a new or editing an existing variable.

    We consistently abbreviate "Variable" to "Var" in this class hierarchy to avoid very long class names (e.g., EditMultiSelectVariableValidator).
